sequenceDiagram
    actor U as Free User
    participant FE as React<br/>MainLayout
    participant Store as useAuthStore
    participant API as DRF<br/>LogoutView
    participant JWT as Token Blacklist

    U->>FE: Click "Logout" button
    FE->>API: POST /api/accounts/logout/ {refresh_token}
    API->>JWT: BlacklistMixin.blacklist(refresh_token)
    JWT-->>API: Token blacklisted
    API-->>FE: 205 Reset Content
    FE->>Store: clearAuth()
    FE-->>U: Redirect to LoginPage
